    <title>Arch Linux Setup</title>
    <link href="/posts/56e4b39.html"/>
    <url>/posts/56e4b39.html</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="密钥登陆，禁用密码"><a href="#密钥登陆，禁用密码" class="headerlink" title="密钥登陆，禁用密码"></a>密钥登陆，禁用密码</h1><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-string">ssh-keygen</span> <span class="hljs-string">-t</span> <span class="hljs-string">ed25519</span> <span class="hljs-string">-b</span> <span class="hljs-number">4096</span><br><br><span class="hljs-string">vim</span> <span class="hljs-string">/etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br><span class="hljs-string">PubkeyAuthentication</span> <span class="hljs-literal">yes</span><br><span class="hljs-string">PasswordAuthentication</span> <span class="hljs-literal">no</span><br><br><span class="hljs-string">sudo</span> <span class="hljs-string">systemctl</span> <span class="hljs-string">restart</span> <span class="hljs-string">sshd.service</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="防火墙-firewalld"><a href="#防火墙-firewalld" class="headerlink" title="防火墙 firewalld"></a>防火墙 firewalld</h1><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">sudo systemctl <span class="hljs-builtin-name">enable</span> firewalld.service<br>sudo systemctl start firewalld.service #不会断开已经链接的端口<br>sudo systemctl restart firewalld.service<br><br>sudo firewall-cmd <span class="hljs-attribute">--zone</span>=public --permanent <span class="hljs-attribute">--add-port</span>=&lt;port&gt;/tcp<br>sudo firewall-cmd <span class="hljs-attribute">--zone</span>=public --permanent <span class="hljs-attribute">--add-port</span>=&lt;port&gt;/udp<br><br>sudo firewall-cmd <span class="hljs-attribute">--zone</span>=public --permanent <span class="hljs-attribute">--remove-port</span>=&lt;port&gt;/tcp<br>sudo firewall-cmd <span class="hljs-attribute">--zone</span>=public --permanent <span class="hljs-attribute">--remove-port</span>=&lt;port&gt;/udp<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="tar"><a href="#tar" class="headerlink" title="tar"></a>tar</h1><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc">tar -zcvf &lt;output&gt; &lt;input&gt;<br><span class="hljs-section">tar -zxvf &lt;input&gt; -C &lt;ouput&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-section">------------------------------</span><br><span class="hljs-code">-c new tar file</span><br><span class="hljs-code">-x extract tar file</span><br><span class="hljs-code">-z gzip</span><br><span class="hljs-code">-v show output</span><br><span class="hljs-code">-f archive name</span><br><span class="hljs-code">-C dir</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="添加-user-到-group"><a href="#添加-user-到-group" class="headerlink" title="添加 user 到 group"></a>添加 user 到 group</h1><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml">usermod -a -G <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">group</span>&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">username</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新登陆</p><h1 id="nginx-mainline"><a href="#nginx-mainline" class="headerlink" title="nginx-mainline"></a>nginx-mainline</h1><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ada">sudo pacman -S nginx-mainline<br>paru -S nginx-mainline-<span class="hljs-keyword">mod</span>-dav-ext<br>paru -S nginx-mainline-<span class="hljs-keyword">mod</span>-fancyindex<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Certbot"><a href="#Certbot" class="headerlink" title="Certbot"></a>Certbot</h1><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">sudo pacman -Syu certbot-nginx</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">vim</span> /etc/nginx/nginx.conf<br>server&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">server_name</span> &lt;domain&gt;;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">listen</span> <span class="hljs-number">80</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight brainfuck"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs brainfuck"><span class="hljs-comment">sudo</span> <span class="hljs-comment">certbot</span> --<span class="hljs-comment">nginx</span> --<span class="hljs-comment">rsa</span><span class="hljs-literal">-</span><span class="hljs-comment">key</span><span class="hljs-literal">-</span><span class="hljs-comment">size</span> <span class="hljs-comment">4096</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="qBittorrent"><a href="#qBittorrent" class="headerlink" title="qBittorrent"></a>qBittorrent</h1><h2 id="qBittorrent-安装和运行"><a href="#qBittorrent-安装和运行" class="headerlink" title="qBittorrent 安装和运行"></a>qBittorrent 安装和运行</h2><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">sudo pacman qbittorrent-nox</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装最新版本的 qBittorrent</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">qbittorrent-nox</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行 qBittorrent</p><p>弹出的提示语表明 WebUI 已经在 localhost:8080 处运行了</p><p>打开浏览器输入地址 + 端口 (例如: 192.168.0.1:8080)</p><p>根据提示语，默认用户名是admin，默认密码是adminadmin</p><p>登陆进去就能看见 qbittorrent 整体的 WebUI 界面了</p><h2 id="配置qBittorrent"><a href="#配置qBittorrent" class="headerlink" title="配置qBittorrent"></a>配置qBittorrent</h2><h3 id="设置语言"><a href="#设置语言" class="headerlink" title="设置语言"></a>设置语言</h3><p>鼠标停在左上角的 Tools -&gt; 点击Options -&gt; 点击Web UI -&gt; English -&gt; 滑倒最底下找到并点击 简体中文 -&gt; 将滚动条滑倒最底下 -&gt; 点击save</p><p>简体中文就设置好了</p><h3 id="配置https"><a href="#配置https" class="headerlink" title="配置https"></a>配置https</h3><p>我们回到arch 的命令行上</p><p>ctrl+c 关掉正在运行 WebUI</p><p>进入 qb 的配置文件夹</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">cd <span class="hljs-regexp">/home/</span>&lt;User&gt;<span class="hljs-regexp">/.config/</span>qBittorrent<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建新的文件夹并进入，此文件夹用来存放证书和密钥</p><figure class="highlight dos"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dos"><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> ssl<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> ssl<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来有两个方法可供选择</p><h4 id="方法1：自己生成密钥（不推荐）"><a href="#方法1：自己生成密钥（不推荐）" class="headerlink" title="方法1：自己生成密钥（不推荐）"></a>方法1：自己生成密钥（不推荐）</h4><h5 id="生成证书和密钥"><a href="#生成证书和密钥" class="headerlink" title="生成证书和密钥"></a>生成证书和密钥</h5><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">openssl</span> req -x<span class="hljs-number">509</span> -newkey rsa:<span class="hljs-number">4096</span> -days <span class="hljs-number">365</span> -keyout server.key -out server.crt -nodes<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此过程会被询问 国家名字，电子邮件什么的。但这些都不需要管，一直按Enter就可以</p><p>运行 ls 命令</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">ls</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>确认有没有 server.crt 和 server.key 这两个文件，有就说明生成成功了</p><p>设置这两个文件为只读权限</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">chmod</span> <span class="hljs-number">400</span> server.crt<br><span class="hljs-attribute">chmod</span> <span class="hljs-number">400</span> server.key<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="使用证书和密钥"><a href="#使用证书和密钥" class="headerlink" title="使用证书和密钥"></a>使用证书和密钥</h5><p>进入 qb 的配置文件</p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino">cd /home/&lt;User&gt;/.config<br>vim qBittorrent.config<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到有 WebUI\HTTPS 前缀的的三个参数并添加或更改它们的值</p><figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gradle">WebuUI\HTTPS\CertificationPath=<span class="hljs-regexp">/home/</span>&lt;User&gt;<span class="hljs-regexp">/.config/</span>qBittorrent<span class="hljs-regexp">/ssl/</span>server.crt<br>WebuUI\HTTPS\Eabled=<span class="hljs-keyword">true</span><br>WebuUI\HTTPS\KeyPath=<span class="hljs-regexp">/home/</span>&lt;User&gt;<span class="hljs-regexp">/.config/</span>qBittorrent<span class="hljs-regexp">/ssl/</span>server.key<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后保存退出 (ESC -&gt; : -&gt; wq -&gt; Enter)</p><h4 id="方法2：使用-letsencrypt-获取证书链（推荐）"><a href="#方法2：使用-letsencrypt-获取证书链（推荐）" class="headerlink" title="方法2：使用 letsencrypt 获取证书链（推荐）"></a>方法2：使用 letsencrypt 获取证书链（推荐）</h4><p>获取到的密钥默认会保存在</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk"><span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>letsencrypt<span class="hljs-regexp">/live/</span>&lt;your.domain&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里会生成4个 .pem 文件</p><p>使用 ls 命令查看（要加sudo），README文件不要管，我们用不着</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">$ sudo ls <span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>letsencrypt<span class="hljs-regexp">/live/</span>&lt;your.domain&gt;<br>$ cert.pem  chain.pem  fullchain.pem  privkey.pem  README<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="H5ai"><a href="#H5ai" class="headerlink" title="H5ai"></a>H5ai</h1><h2 id="nginx"><a href="#nginx" class="headerlink" title="nginx"></a>nginx</h2><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">location / &#123;<br><span class="hljs-regexp">/h5ai/</span>_h5ai<span class="hljs-regexp">/public/i</span>ndex.php<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启 nginx 服务</p><figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs maxima">sudo systemctl <span class="hljs-built_in">restart</span> nginx.service<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="主页面加密码："><a href="#主页面加密码：" class="headerlink" title="主页面加密码："></a>主页面加密码：</h2><p><a href="https://www.tok9.com/archives/386/">https://www.tok9.com/archives/386/</a></p><h2 id="public-index-php-加密码"><a href="#public-index-php-加密码" class="headerlink" title="public/index.php 加密码"></a>public/index.php 加密码</h2><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">head <span class="hljs-regexp">/dev/u</span>random | tr -dc A-Za-z0-<span class="hljs-number">9</span> | head -c length ; echo <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#随机字符串</span><br>echo -n <span class="hljs-string">&quot;密码&quot;</span> |sha512sum<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="extensions"><a href="#extensions" class="headerlink" title="extensions"></a>extensions</h3><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">sudo pacman -S imagick # 安装 imagemagick (PDF thumbs)<br>sudo pacman -S ffmpeg<br><br>sudo vim /etc/php/php.ini<br><span class="hljs-builtin-name">enable</span><br>gd<br>zip<br>exif<br><span class="hljs-builtin-name">add</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">extension</span>=imagick<br>sudo systemctl restart php-fpm.service<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="内网-前缀"><a href="#内网-前缀" class="headerlink" title="内网 - 前缀"></a>内网 - 前缀</h1><p><a href="https://library.marmot.website/">https://library.marmot.website/</a></p><p>路径：</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk"><span class="hljs-regexp">/usr/</span>share<span class="hljs-regexp">/nginx/</span>html/library<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="AriaNg"><a href="#AriaNg" class="headerlink" title="AriaNg"></a>AriaNg</h1><h2 id="下载最新-release-包"><a href="#下载最新-release-包" class="headerlink" title="下载最新 release 包"></a>下载最新 release 包</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/mayswind/AriaNg/releases">Releases · mayswind/AriaNg (github.com)</a></p><h2 id="运行"><a href="#运行" class="headerlink" title="运行"></a>运行</h2><p>aria2c –conf-path=PATH</p><hr><h1 id="参考内容"><a href="#参考内容" class="headerlink" title="参考内容"></a>参考内容</h1><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/51bd2b82ff35">Linux设置密钥登录 - 简书 (jianshu.com)</a></p><p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/w3cnote/set-ssh-login-key.html">设置 SSH 通过密钥登录 | 菜鸟教程 (runoob.com)</a></p><p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/linux/linux-shell.html">Shell 教程 | 菜鸟教程 (runoob.com)</a></p><p><a href="https://www.yisu.com/help/id_104.html">SSL安全证书证书安装_中间证书/证书链安装指南 - 帮助文档 - 亿速云 (yisu.com)</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
